---
---

<section class="how" id="how" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
  <header class="how-head" data-animate>
    <p class="kicker">Getting started</p>
    <h2 id="how-heading">Up and running in an afternoon.</h2>
    <p class="sub">No new workflow to invent. Amprealize fits around how your team already moves.</p>
  </header>

  <ol class="timeline" data-animate style="transition-delay: 60ms">
    <li class="timeline-item">
      <span class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Connect your workspace</h3>
        <p>Set up projects and boards, bring in your team, and wire agents with <code>npx @amprealize/cli wizard</code>. Done in minutes.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="timeline-item">
      <span class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Work flows between humans and agents</h3>
        <p>Assign tasks to teammates — human or AI. Agents run, post results to the board, and hand off to a human the moment judgment is needed.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="timeline-item">
      <span class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Patterns become team assets</h3>
        <p>Good runs get extracted into versioned behaviors. Your library grows sprint over sprint, so every future project starts with everything you already know.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>

<style>
  .how {
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: var(--landing-section-y, clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px));
  }

  .how-head {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .kicker {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent-secondary);
  }

  .how-head h2 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1.6vw + 0.4rem, 1.7rem);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
  }

  .sub {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .timeline {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 19px;
    top: 12px;
    bottom: 12px;
    width: 2px;
    background: rgba(73, 112, 146, 0.2);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    padding: var(--space-5) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .step-num {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: #fff;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-bg-app);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(2) .step-num {
    background: var(--color-accent-secondary);
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(3) .step-num {
    background: var(--color-info);
  }

  .step-body {
    min-width: 0;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .step-body h3 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
  }

  .step-body p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .timeline::before {
      left: 15px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
    }
  }
</style>
